 n&agrave;o c&ograve;n thừa th&igrave; đại lượng đ&oacute; nhiều hơn.</p>', '2019-11-06 23:08:49', '2019-11-06 23:08:49'),
(25, 7, 1, '<p style=\"text-align:center\">Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n n&agrave;o dưới đ&acirc;y bằng với số quả d&acirc;u t&acirc;y trong h&igrave;nh ?</p>', '<div class=\"image-group\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293782975_dau_tay.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:50px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293782975_dau_tay.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:50px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293782975_dau_tay.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:50px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293782975_dau_tay.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:50px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293782975_dau_tay.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:50px\" title=\"\" /></div>', NULL, '<div class=\"image-group\"><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293111216_chuoi.png\" style=\"height:100px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293111216_chuoi.png\" style=\"height:100px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293111216_chuoi.png\" style=\"height:100px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293111216_chuoi.png\" style=\"height:100px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /></div>', '<div class=\"image-group\"><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293191022_bi_vang.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293191022_bi_vang.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293191022_bi_vang.png\" style=\"height:70px; width:70px\" title=\"\" /><img class=\"image-item\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1543293191022_bi_vang.p