(26, 8, 1, '<p style=\"text-align:center\">H&igrave;nh n&agrave;o dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng ?</p>', NULL, NULL, '<div class=\"image-group\"><img class=\"image-item\" height=\"null\" width=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1539934456230_2.1.png\" title=\"\"></div>', '<div class=\"image-group\"><img class=\"image-item\" height=\"null\" width=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1539934474185_2.2.png\" title=\"\"></div>', '<div class=\"image-group\"><img class=\"image-item\" height=\"null\" width=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1539934828924_2.3.png\" title=\"\"></div>', '<div class=\"image-group\"><img class=\"image-item\" height=\"null\" width=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1539934851254_2.4.png\" title=\"\"></div>', '3', NULL, '<p>Phương ph&aacute;p giải</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quan s&aacute;t h&igrave;nh vẽ v&agrave; x&aacute;c định h&igrave;nh vu&ocirc;ng c&oacute; trong c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh đ&atilde; cho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vungoi.vn/vungoi/1536569159704_5.png\" title=\"\" /></p>', '2019-11-06 23:23:52', '2019-11-06 23:23:52'),
